Token.Abstract: Add this class to your Watch App Extension.
Starts an instance of the TEALWKExtension.

Parameter.Name: key
Parameter.Abstract: A unique string identifier for the target matching Tealium instance.

Parameter.Name: configuration
Parameter.Abstract: A TEALWKExtensionConfiguration object that contains the target account-profile-env settings.

ReturnValue.Abstract: TEALWKExtension instance that matches a Tealium instance with the given configuration

Token.Abstract: NSString identifier for the library extension instance.

Parameter.Name: key
Parameter.Abstract: NSString identifier for the library extension instance.

ReturnValue.Abstract: An instance of the TEALWKExtension for calling methods.

Token.Abstract: Removes and nils out an instance of the extension library. Thread-safe.
Sends an event to Collect. Event are packaged with any custom key/value data sources passed in along with the default datasources provided by the library. Thread-safe.

Parameter.Name: customDataSources
Parameter.Abstract: Dictionary of custom datasources (key/value pairs) to be included in the event dispatch. If a value is an array, be sure to use an array of strings.

Token.Abstract: Sends a view to Collect. Views are packaged with any custom key/value data sources passed in along with the default datasources provided by the library. Thread-safe.

Parameter.Name: customDataSources
Parameter.Abstract: Dictionary of custom datasources (key/value pairs) to be included in the event dispatch. If a value is an array, be sure to use an array of strings.
